songs.title: Day Ones
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Yeah yeah yeah
Thugger, YG, and Nipsey, Hussle
Yeah
Yeah
Real spit, pay attention

[Pre-Chorus]
I ain't never switched up on my day ones (Ayy)
I ain't never switched up on my day ones
Nah, I ain't never switched up on my day ones
I never never switched up on my day ones (Ayy ayy ayy)

[Chorus]
Keep your foot on the asphalt
You get caught that's your mans fault
You get blamed that's you mans fault
Keep your foot on the asphalt yeah
Bang that thing like your dad taught you (Yeah)
Diamonds bling that's [?] fault
Jimmy dean what I'm eating, yeah yeah
I want wings get me weed yeah yeah

[Verse 1]
I get fly like propellers nigga
I'm booked up check the schedule nigga
Told my hoe she need a better nigga (What?)
She'll only do what you tell her, nigga
My background go bling like a bezel nigga
I make it rain bring your umbrella with you (Throw it)
I can't make you famous no fucking pictures
My single went gold like a fucking treasure (Woo)
I'm keeping my homies behind me
I done lost my heart, I can't find it
I know these hoes tryna define me
I'm lookin' down, I see them climbing (You know it)
Don't grab me on me bitch or they shootin' at your fingers
I'm feedin' them semens
I love my nigga to death because everything we go through don't never get between us (Swear)
Okay I froze em, they frozen (Frozen)
They blood and they rollin' (Yeah)
Catch up like a slow poke, you Yoshi (Jaha)
Just riding round town like tryna expose 'em
And I bought some cake and you know you can take some cause

[Pre-Chorus]
I ain't never switched up on my day ones (Ayy)
I ain't never switched up on my day ones
Nah, I ain't never switched up on my day ones
I never  never switched up on my day ones (Ayy ayy)

[Chorus: Young Thug]
Keep your foot on the asphalt (Skrrt)
You get caught that's your mans fault
You get blamed that's you mans fault
Keep your foot on the asphalt (Yeah yeah yeah)
Bang that thing like your dad taught you
Diamonds bling that's [?]
Jimmy dean what I'm eating, yeah yeah
I want wings get me weed yeah yeah
